name: Marron nature
description:
French Woven Chestnut Garden Chairs accompany our oak dining tables well. That's why we offer them in our shop. 
At first natural color, but weathers nicely into perfect grey.

These authentic garden chairs are entirely made ​​from chestnut branches. Using different sizes of braided chestnut.  This balck version has not been peeled. More natural. 

They support a little summer rain. However, to enjoy as long as possible, it is advisable to put them sheltered. Sous l'abris to be more precise.
